  <body>
    <div class="m-3 p-3 border rounded-3 shadow">
      <h5><span class="badge text-bg-info">Info</span></h5>
      <h1 id="help">Help</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to ShoeTronics, the online store where you can find the best
        deals on shoes and electronic devices. We are here to help you with any
        questions or issues you may have regarding our products and services.
        Please read the following sections to find the answers you need.
      </p>
      <h2 id="how-to-order">How to order</h2>
      <p>
        To order from ShoeTronics, you need to create an account with us. You
        can do this by clicking on the "Sign up" button on the top right corner
        of our website. You will need to provide your name, email address,
        password, and shipping address. Once you have an account, you can browse
        our catalog of shoes and electronic devices by category, brand, price,
        size, color, or rating. You can also use the search bar to find specific
        items. When you find something you like, you can add it to your cart by
        clicking on the "Add to cart" button. You can view your cart at any time
        by clicking on the "Cart" icon on the top right corner of our website.
        When you are ready to check out, click on the "Proceed to checkout"
        button and follow the instructions to complete your payment and confirm
        your order.
      </p>
      <h2 id="shipping-and-delivery">Shipping and delivery</h2>
      <p>
        We offer free standard shipping for all orders over $50 within the
        United States. Standard shipping takes 3-5 business days to arrive. You
        can also choose expedited shipping for an extra fee, which takes 1-2
        business days to arrive. We ship internationally as well, but the
        shipping cost and delivery time may vary depending on your location and
        customs regulations. You can track your order status and delivery date
        by logging into your account and clicking on the "Orders" tab. You will
        also receive an email confirmation with a tracking number when your
        order is shipped.
      </p>
      <h2 id="returns-and-refunds">Returns and refunds</h2>
      <p>
        We want you to be happy with your purchase from ShoeTronics. If for any
        reason you are not satisfied with your order, you can return it within
        30 days of delivery for a full refund or exchange. The items must be in
        their original condition, unworn, unused, and with their original
        packaging and tags. To initiate a return or exchange, please contact our
        customer service team at support@shoetronics.com or call us at
        1-800-555-1234. We will provide you with a prepaid return label and
        instructions on how to send back your items. Once we receive your
        return, we will process your refund or exchange within 7 business days.
      </p>
      <h2 id="customer-service">Customer service</h2>
      <p>
        We are here to help you with any questions or issues you may have
        regarding our products and services. You can contact our customer
        service team by email at support@shoetronics.com or by phone at
        1-800-555-1234. Our business hours are Monday-Friday from 9 am to 5 pm
        EST. You can also chat with us online by clicking on the "Chat" button
        on the bottom right corner of our website. We will respond to your
        inquiries as soon as possible.
      </p>
      <h2 id="feedback">Feedback</h2>
      <p>
        We value your feedback and suggestions on how we can improve our
        products and services. Please feel free to leave us a review on our
        website or social media platforms. You can also email us at
        feedback@shoetronics.com or fill out our online survey. We appreciate
        your support and loyalty.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing ShoeTronics!</p>
